meaning to do something to stop it rotting so it can be eaten later.

90
00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:32.800
No meds are people who travel from one place to another,

91
00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:37.200
often with animal livestock, rather than living in one place all the time.

92
00:05:37.200 --> 00:05:41.800
Dairy products are food such as cheese and butter, which are made from milk.

93
00:05:41.800 --> 00:05:48.400
If you take a step back, you temporarily remove yourself from a situation in order to reevaluate it.

94
00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:55.800
The idiom to look at the bigger picture means to consider the overall meaning of something rather than the specific details.

95
00:05:55.800 --> 00:06:02.800
And finally, the adjective premature describes something which happens too soon or before the proper time.

96
